<template>
<svg width="150" height="120" viewBox="0 0 120 80" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="empty-map-svg">
    <g>
        <!-- 简约地图轮廓 -->
        <path class="map-outline" d="M20,60 Q30,30 60,20 Q90,30 100,60 Q80,70 60,65 Q40,70 20,60 Z" />
        <!-- 动态区域填充 -->
        <path class="map-fill" d="M30,58 Q38,38 60,30 Q82,38 90,58 Q78,64 60,61 Q42,64 30,58 Z" />
        <!-- 标记点 -->
        <circle class="map-dot" cx="60" cy="45" r="4" />
        <circle class="map-dot" cx="75" cy="50" r="2.5" />
        <circle class="map-dot" cx="48" cy="55" r="2.5" />
    </g>
</svg>
</template>

<script setup>
</script>

<style scoped>
.empty-map-svg { display: block; margin: 0 auto; animation: floatX 4.2s ease-in-out infinite; }
.map-outline {
    fill: none;
    stroke: #A0C4FF;
    stroke-width: 2.5;
    opacity: 0.6;
}
.map-fill {
  fill: #4F8EF7;
  opacity: 0.18;
  transform: scaleY(0.2);
  transform-origin: 60px 60px;
  animation: map-fill-grow 2.2s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) infinite;
}
@keyframes map-fill-grow {
  0% { transform: scaleY(0.2); opacity: 0.12; }
  18% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.7; }
  80% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.7; }
  100% { transform: scaleY(0.2); opacity: 0.12; }
}
.map-dot {
  fill: #FFB300;
  opacity: 0.7;
  animation: map-dot-pop 2.2s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) infinite;
}
@keyframes map-dot-pop {
  0% { opacity: 0.2; transform: scale(0.5); }
  20% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.2); }
  60% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  100% { opacity: 0.2; transform: scale(0.5); }
}
@keyframes floatX {
  0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
  25% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-12px) translateX(-4px); }
  75% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
  100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
}
</style>
